  m_Name: Dungeons_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 96480256c1342c74dbf61483e4a515b4, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items:
      Array:
      - rid: 5955913234500026484
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 11823947247616
    m_Localized: '{GlobalKeywords.Village}'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array:
        - rid: 5955913234500026484
  - m_Id: 11824022745088
    m_Localized: The village of Gorton, a sleepy, parochial place. Don't let its tranquil exterior fool you. This is a melting pot for heroes and heroines! An adventurer's terminus quo.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745089
    m_Localized: Mad Forest
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745090
    m_Localized: Once a thriving haven, now a dumping ground for evil. A vampire is said to be the root of this evil, but we can find only mayhem and roast chicken.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745091
    m_Localized: Inlaid Library
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745092
    m_Localized: The Futile Scribe was cursed to know all and understand nothing. His endless library may gift us insight... or damnation. A mask of stone whispers endlessly within.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745093
    m_Localized: Dairy Plant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745094
    m_Localized: The birthplace of Milk Magic churns with chaos. Here, it's not just blood that curdles. A Creamy Surprise awaits the hero brave enough to enter this overthrown factory.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745095
    m_Localized: Gallo Tower
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745096
    m_Localized: An edifice of science and sorcery where horror was made manifest in the name of progress. Its many artifacts and experiments may lead us to what we seek.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745097
    m_Localized: Cappella Magna
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 11824022745098
    m_Localized: Conceited were they that ruled from so high yet stooped so low. This nexus of debased purity is the perfect place to find a vampire. Probably.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 5409240946401281
    m_Localized: Teeny Bridge
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 5409240946401282
    m_Localized: This handsome little bridge seems perfectly safe to cross. Definitely better than swimming, anyway.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 5409240946401283
    m_Localized: Weeny Bridge
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 5409240946401284
    m_Localized: This bridge seems even smaller and quieter than the last one. No doubt this time it will be safe to cross in peace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 5409240946401285
    m_Localized: Meany Bridge
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 5409240946401286
    m_Localized: An innocent looking bridge with an intimidating name. What could possibly go wrong?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 12266632501878784
    m_Localized: Furious Forest
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 12266632527044608
    m_Localized: The deeper the forest goes the more unsettling the monsters become. Something in the air must be pushing them to insanity.. Dark magic or maybe the quality of the chicken.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 12266632527044609
    m_Localized: Berserk Wood
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 12266632527044610
    m_Localized: There is no turning back from the depths once inside. A muffled cry can be heard between the trees, along with the flapping of a thousand wings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002012160000
    m_Localized: Library West Wing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714432
    m_Localized: No sane intruder would dare talk louder than a whisper, in this labyrinth of book shelves and cursed tomes.  Inhuman forms stalk the halls, seeking long overdue revenge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714433
    m_Localized: Library Sanctum
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714434
    m_Localized: Once home to some of the world's brightest and most talented mages. Now there is nothing but dark magic, vile familiars and those who seek to control them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714435
    m_Localized: Milk Factory
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714436
    m_Localized: In days gone by, corrupt officials skimmed off the top to line their pockets. Now all that remains is a maze of pipes, haunted by the huge golems which once protected this place.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714437
    m_Localized: Curd Refinery
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714438
    m_Localized: The epicenter of the Dairy industrial complex, where many a cheesy adventurer has lost their whey.  Beware the milk-crazed beasts and raw milky magic.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714439
    m_Localized: Cappella Ultima
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 40868002045714440
    m_Localized: Here lies the floating throne room. Where the puppet masters of all this land’s woes dangle their strings. A fitting perch for those who fancy themselves gods yet wallow in rot.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  - m_Id: 96305600638476288
    m_Localized: (marker to show the expected end of the sheet)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
        Array: []
  references: {}
